<td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Word drops</span><hr size=1> Ok, I know this may not be the best forum to post this, but i havent got many responses in other areas. The problem is this; I am almost lvl 31 now. I went all the way thru 24-29 with the earth pet only because I could only find two words of dimension. I burned those up in failed reseach attemps. I have only found one word of coercion and i  bought that in the bazaar. Other mesg forums I have seen say to hunt in lvl appropriate zones. I do. I have also been to vendors from velious to Odus to the moon looking for these friggin things. No luck. WTF?!!? Am i doomed to never use my researched pets? Im in double jeopardy now. Even if I find more words of coercion, I still have to find the words of dimension to make the lvl 29 pets.<br>
<br>
Is anyone else having this problem? I am on the Luclin server. Is this a problem on all servers? It is getting so frustrating I am considering sending a petition to a GM (a whole lotta good that will do!?!).<br>
<br>
Again, sorry for putting this here. I saw the post on the Gorla word drops and decided to post here.<br>
<br>
Take Care, <br>
<br>
Aeedar Incantus<br>
Mage of the 30th season<br>
